text: avara janangadavaru avara balige dhavisi bandaru. Avaru i hinde papa karyagalalli todagiddaru. Avaru (lut) helidaru; nanna janangadavare, ivaru nanna putriyaru. Nim'ma palige ivaru heccu pavanaragiddare. Nivu allahanige anjiri mattu nanna atithigala naduve nannannu apamanisabedi. Nim'malli caritrya sari iruva obba purusanu illave
